{
  "stem": "26142.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And at that time, they were going from Romania to the Black Sea, into the-- the Dardanelles and the Mediterranean.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That must have taken him-- I don't know how long it took at that time to get-- to get to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He came and settled in Jerusalem.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he was-- he lived there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He died in 1917.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He lived 14 years after-- after he emigrated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And when I-- I was in Israel visiting, five, six years ago, I-- I managed to-- to find somebody that was taking care-- has the books of the cemetery of the [NON-ENGLISH], of the Mount of Olives.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I asked him to look up the name.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he found the name and the date and everything-- when he-- when he died.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My older brothers, Eliezer and-- and Moshe, were-- were-- they always used to brag that they were very proud that they got their grandfather-- their great-grandfather sent them Tefillin.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When they got bar mitzvah'd-- well, they were bar mitzvah'd already-- he was already in Israel-- in Israel-- in Palestine, Jerusalem a few years.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They-- he sent them Tefillin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were very proud of that, that they got Tefillin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We also used to talk-- I remember now, our house-- that for some time they would for the holiday of Sukkot, that he would send a-- a-- a esrog.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know what an esrog is?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "An esrog and lulav, that-- this was very unique at that time, that you had an esrog coming from Israel.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not like now, that you put it on the plane, and they bring it over here.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's here.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in those years-- What was your involvement in the Zionist movement?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I was a Zionist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I believed in it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I also wanted-- wanted to-- to leave.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
